Definition: weedy trailing mat-forming herb with bright yellow flowers cultivated for its edible mildly acid leaves eaten raw or cooked especially in Indian and Greek and Middle Eastern cuisine
Example: cosmopolitan
Synonyms: pussley, pussly, verdolagas, Portulaca_oleracea, purslane, genus_Portulaca, m, weedy, trailing, mat-forming, herb, with, bright, yellow, flowers, cultivated, for, its, edible, mildly, acid, leaves, eaten, raw, or, cooked, especially, in, Indian, and, Greek, Middle, Eastern, cuisine, cosmopolitan
Category: noun.plant
